            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-12/file7ioh0u82fx21hl7rhiq0.jpg?VersionId=dcDOigKysUxWjg8oNIHiNnbQpAqzO3pN&itok=i92fGrr9" title="12月3日，中老铁路首发列车抵达中国磨憨站。（新华社）" alt="12月3日，中老铁路首发列车抵达中国磨憨站。（新华社）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-12/file7ioh0u82fx21hl7rhiq0.jpg?VersionId=dcDOigKysUxWjg8oNIHiNnbQpAqzO3pN&itok=i92fGrr9" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
